that it's a lot easier to understand.

15:06.505 --> 15:08.005
Very well. Here?

15:08.755 --> 15:09.713
Ready?

15:10.047 --> 15:11.005
Yes.

15:13.130 --> 15:14.588
<i>My dearest daughters...</i>

15:15.172 --> 15:18.838
