<i>that means I'm no longer by your side.</i>

15:20.088 --> 15:22.213
<i>And that is why I want to tell you...</i>

15:23.838 --> 15:26.713
<i>you are the best thing</i>
<i>that ever happened to me.</i>

15:27.255 --> 15:28.213
<i>The best.</i>

15:29.213 --> 15:31.088
<i>You have filled me with happiness.</i>

15:32.047 --> 15:35.672
<i>You have given me so many memories.</i>
<i>You have made me so proud.</i>

15:36.880 --> 15:40.338
<i>Maybe I wasn't the best mom in the world.</i>

15:41.047 --> 15:42.547
<i>But I feel fulfilled.</i>

15:43.505 --> 15:45.713
<i>There is just one thing that...</i>

15:46.588 --> 15:48.755
<i>I have always carried with me.</i>

15:49.713 --> 15:51.755
<i>That I never dared to confess.</i>

15:53.005 --> 15:54.880
<i>But I don't want to take it to my grave.</i>

15:56.297 --> 15:58.422
<i>Because it has to do with all of you.</i>

15:59.172 --> 16:03.338
<i>I have always kept your real roots</i>
<i>hidden from you.</i>

16:03.422 --> 16:06.172
<i>Today is the day</i>
<i>that I confess to you that Dad...</i>

16:07.713 --> 16:08.588
<i>Pedro...</i>

16:09.172 --> 16:11.672
