why I didn't belong in this fucking house.

20:19.380 --> 20:22.047
So what do we do? Do we search or not?

20:26.005 --> 20:27.088
Let's see.

20:31.672 --> 20:32.838
-Here?
-Yeah.

20:32.922 --> 20:34.088
