What's this guy's name again?

40:41.463 --> 40:43.172
I am Father Díaz.

40:43.755 --> 40:46.047
I appreciate you coming here
to pay me a visit.

40:46.755 --> 40:52.088
I guess you know your mom
refused to let me see any of you.

40:52.172 --> 40:53.880
Yeah, we are aware of that.

40:56.838 --> 40:59.547
Meeting you at last is a blessing for me.

40:59.630 --> 41:02.255
I've prayed to God for this day.

41:02.547 --> 41:05.755
I also asked God to look out for you.

41:07.338 --> 41:10.838
Father, I thought you guys couldn't...

41:10.922 --> 41:13.047
-No, she means...
-...do it.

41:13.130 --> 41:16.755
We just didn't expect you to be...

41:16.838 --> 41:18.380
-A monk, right?
-Exactly.

41:18.463 --> 41:20.838
-This way.
-And blind. A blind monk.

41:20.922 --> 41:23.005
Blind people do it too, you know?

41:23.088 --> 41:25.213
He can still hear you!

41:25.547 --> 41:27.005
I still remember her.

41:27.755 --> 41:29.047
Those curves...

41:30.130 --> 41:31.380
That smile...

41:31.963 --> 41:33.922
The beautiful way she moved.

41:34.005 --> 41:38.505
-Father, you're getting off the point.
-Yeah.

41:38.755 --> 41:41.713
-We're trying to find our dad, remember?
-One of them.

41:41.797 --> 41:44.547
-Yeah.
-Oh, right. Forgive me.

41:44.922 --> 41:46.255
The thing is...

41:47.713 --> 41:50.755
when I confessed my feelings to her,

41:51.130 --> 41:53.088
rather than slap me,

41:53.422 --> 41:56.505
Carmen offered to sleep with me.

41:58.130 --> 42:00.047
All this is so shocking.

42:00.130 --> 42:02.838
-And I'm supposed to be the loose one.
-Shit, me too.

42:02.922 --> 42:04.380
It happened only once, but...

42:05.505 --> 42:07.755
it was enough to meet her needs.

42:09.463 --> 42:15.172
Months later, she wrote me a letter,
thanking me for my collaboration.

42:17.880 --> 42:21.588
But I had already given myself to the Lord
and I couldn't pull out of it.

42:21.672 --> 42:23.505
Sure, pull out, right?

42:25.588 --> 42:29.630
We know that moment meant a lot to you.

42:29.713 --> 42:33.005
-So you probably remember the date, right?
-Sure, how could I forget?

42:33.630 --> 42:36.422
It was April 2, 1985.

42:36.963 --> 42:41.505
We made love from 6:55 to 6:60 a.m.

42:42.005 --> 42:44.672
-I mean, 7:00.
-Don't count, it's Sofía.

42:48.630 --> 42:50.213
-Father...
-My girl!

42:50.297 --> 42:51.380
-No...
-My girl.

42:51.755 --> 42:55.672
-No, she is your daughter. Sorry.
-Oh, my daughter!

42:55.755 --> 42:58.130
-It's not me. It's her.
-Not her, either.

42:58.213 --> 43:00.297
My daughter.

43:02.297 --> 43:03.380
Let me...

43:04.547 --> 43:08.547
I always imagined
that you'd be this beautiful.

43:09.797 --> 43:11.630
Let me give you a hug.

43:16.172 --> 43:17.422
My girl.

43:19.213 --> 43:22.380
-My girl!
-It's the marijuana.

43:24.130 --> 43:27.630
-I don't know if it's a good idea.
-What? Come on, it would be appropriate.

43:27.963 --> 43:30.130
-She knows who her father is. We don't.
-I know.

43:30.213 --> 43:35.297
Sara, that guy is creepy.
But she just has to go and do it. It's OK.

43:36.797 --> 43:37.922
You tell her, then.

43:38.380 --> 43:39.213
Me?

43:43.130 --> 43:44.547
-<i>Hello.</i>
-Hey!

43:45.630 --> 43:46.547
Finally.

43:47.422 --> 43:49.713
I thought you didn't want
to talk to me anymore.

43:54.588 --> 43:55.505
Marta...

43:58.255 --> 43:59.213
Listen...

43:59.797 --> 44:01.130
I know you are...

44:01.797 --> 44:03.963
expecting something from me
that I may not...

44:04.380 --> 44:06.005
<i>No, it's my fault.</i>

44:08.547 --> 44:09.713
Why do you say that?

44:10.005 --> 44:11.838
Because I got my hopes up, Sofía.

44:13.047 --> 44:15.838
<i>I think we might get engaged</i>
<i>at any moment and...</i>

44:16.630 --> 44:18.130
<i>And then you disappear.</i>

44:18.672 --> 44:20.547
<i>And I don't hear from you again.</i>

44:22.755 --> 44:23.797
Marta...

44:24.255 --> 44:26.338
You have no idea how hard this has been.

44:28.672 --> 44:30.630
<i>I won't be here forever, Sofía.</i>

44:32.172 --> 44:33.088
<i>I know.</i>

44:35.338 --> 44:36.463
We'll talk tomorrow.

44:38.422 --> 44:39.505
Till tomorrow.

44:45.630 --> 44:46.505
Hi.

44:48.338 --> 44:49.172
Hey.

44:51.797 --> 44:52.838
How are you?

44:53.797 --> 44:55.380
I'm not sure.

44:56.547 --> 44:58.797
-I thought things would go differently.
-Right.

44:59.547 --> 45:01.505
I am a lesbian. An atheist.

45:02.380 --> 45:03.797
With a priest for a father.

45:04.130 --> 45:06.338
-It seems like a joke.
-It kind of does.

45:08.880 --> 45:11.172
But, at least you know now
who your father is.

45:11.797 --> 45:12.838
Right?

45:15.838 --> 45:16.963
Tell her now.

45:23.713 --> 45:26.713
-What's going on?
-We need you, that's all.

45:27.005 --> 45:30.797
We need your help. Pablo isn't your dad,
so only you can do something for us.

45:30.880 --> 45:33.130
Go to his studio
and get a sample of his DNA.

45:33.880 --> 45:36.255
You heard him. He doesn't care for tests.

45:36.338 --> 45:39.338
Right. But while we were there,
we also saw that...

45:39.422 --> 45:42.380
-Yes.
-...he kind of liked you.

45:42.463 --> 45:45.922
-Exactly.
-We thought you could go and talk to him.

45:46.005 --> 45:49.130
Yes, and then you could get
a nail from him.

45:49.630 --> 45:51.172
Or a tiny hair.

45:51.255 --> 45:53.797
-Of course, or a hair.
-It could be...

45:53.880 --> 45:56.922
A gum chewed by him would work too.

45:57.005 --> 45:59.797
-A small thing.
-It would work genetically speaking.

46:00.463 --> 46:01.880
-You're kidding.
-We're not.

46:01.963 --> 46:06.088
It would be easier for you to pose
for him and get a hair from him.

46:06.172 --> 46:07.588
That's all.

46:07.672 --> 46:10.172
And we'll go on with the rest.

46:10.255 --> 46:13.380
Also, you can get a painting for free.
Think about that.

46:14.547 --> 46:16.088
I have my own paintings.

46:16.713 --> 46:19.088
Did you see what that guy draws? Nudes.

46:19.338 --> 46:22.797
Right, but you're so open-minded.
You are OK with that.

46:23.630 --> 46:27.422
Yeah, I'm open-minded. But you want me
to get naked in front of one of your dads?

46:27.713 --> 46:29.880
-I don't mind if he sees you naked.
-Me neither.

46:29.963 --> 46:31.172
-I also don't.
-Not at all.

46:31.255 --> 46:34.213
You getting naked
in front of a possible dad of mine

46:34.297 --> 46:36.130
wouldn't bother me at all.

46:36.213 --> 46:37.838
You know what? That's not the issue.

46:37.922 --> 46:41.088
The issue is none of this makes any sense.
And you're all crazy.

46:48.505 --> 46:51.505
Come on, Sofía. The answer is in his DNA.

46:52.213 --> 46:55.130
Also, think about getting this
all over with.

46:55.213 --> 46:56.505
I don't know. Please.

47:00.338 --> 47:01.672
Do it for us.

47:03.338 --> 47:04.505
Come on.

47:12.713 --> 47:14.797
See? Not everything had to be thrown away.

47:14.880 --> 47:16.172
What do you mean, Claudia?

47:16.630 --> 47:19.838
Mom didn't only sleep
with hippies and priests.

47:19.922 --> 47:20.922
I hope so.

47:21.505 --> 47:23.505
This guy is elegant, I'm telling you.

47:23.588 --> 47:27.505
-We can't know that. We don't know him.
-You can smell that sort of thing.

47:27.588 --> 47:29.922
-Hello.
-Good afternoon.

47:30.005 --> 47:33.172
We have an appointment with Mr. Víctor...

47:33.255 --> 47:35.005
-Nozal.
-Víctor Nozal.

47:35.422 --> 47:37.047
-I'll let him know.
-OK.

47:37.755 --> 47:40.005
-Go to the seventh floor.
-Thank you.

47:41.505 --> 47:43.297
Carrara marble. Impressive.

47:49.380 --> 47:50.963
Hello. Are you Víctor?

47:51.047 --> 47:52.880
-That's right.
-Hello.

47:52.963 --> 47:54.047
-My pleasure.
-Mine too.

47:54.422 --> 47:55.922
-Hello.
-Please.

47:56.463 --> 47:58.005
-Please.
-Let's go to my office.

47:58.672 --> 48:00.838
By the way, this building is stunning.

48:00.922 --> 48:03.797
Yeah, it was one of my first projects
as an architect.

48:04.422 --> 48:09.547
I wanted to showcase the architectural
waves that stuck with me as a student.

48:09.630 --> 48:10.547
Fabulous.

48:12.880 --> 48:15.463
Please, have a seat.
Would you like a drink?

48:15.880 --> 48:16.797
-No.
-Yes.

48:17.297 --> 48:20.713
That Cabernet Sauvignon is my favorite.

48:20.797 --> 48:21.672
Very well.

48:23.588 --> 48:24.672
Your mother...

48:25.713 --> 48:29.797
She was from another world.
I asked her to marry me many times but...

48:30.547 --> 48:32.922
But she told me she'd never leave Pedro.

48:33.130 --> 48:36.297
I never understood how she could be
so passionate in bed with me...

48:36.797 --> 48:38.547
then go back to another man.

48:38.630 --> 48:42.422
You can spare us the details, really.
Thanks.

48:43.047 --> 48:45.088
Well, marriage is overrated

48:45.172 --> 48:48.380
and there are less and less honest people
in the world.

49:06.172 --> 49:07.713
Víctor, are you all right?

49:07.797 --> 49:09.922
You came for the truth...

49:11.172 --> 49:13.255
and here I am, lying to you.

49:13.963 --> 49:15.047
Shit, come on.

49:16.672 --> 49:19.713
This office. This suit.
None of it is mine.

49:19.797 --> 49:21.588
Not even the shoes I'm wearing.

49:21.672 --> 49:24.297
But you are Víctor?
You were our mother's lover.

49:24.380 --> 49:26.755
Yes, but I'm not the architect
of this building.

49:27.963 --> 49:29.005
I'm just...

49:30.297 --> 49:31.630
...the janitor.

49:31.880 --> 49:34.047
And I clean the offices on weekends.

49:34.630 --> 49:36.588
Do you think we're in the mood for this?

49:37.463 --> 49:39.005
I didn't want my daughter...

49:39.797 --> 49:41.797
to know that I'm a failure.

49:42.213 --> 49:45.297
A man who lost everything
to gambling and drink.

49:45.380 --> 49:48.505
Do you mean you are a homeless man?

49:49.172 --> 49:53.755
Can you remember the dates
when you had relations with our mother?

49:53.838 --> 49:57.963
Well, our relationship lasted for years,
but not continually.

49:58.213 --> 50:00.797
OK, so anyone of us
could be your daughter, right?

50:01.172 --> 50:02.338
No, not just anyone.

50:04.547 --> 50:05.755
Only she...

50:07.005 --> 50:08.380
who bears my mother's name.

50:09.547 --> 50:11.380
What is your mother's name?

50:12.922 --> 50:13.838
Claudia.

50:31.588 --> 50:32.505
It's me.

50:32.588 --> 50:33.838
I'm Claudia.

50:34.880 --> 50:35.922
My girl.

50:56.380 --> 50:57.797
I love the studio.

50:58.630 --> 50:59.505
It's wonderful.

51:00.463 --> 51:01.297
Yeah.

51:03.422 --> 51:05.463
And I love the fact
that I'm not your father.

51:05.547 --> 51:08.755
Why don't you lie down? Stretched out.

51:09.463 --> 51:10.588
It's more elegant.

51:11.797 --> 51:14.505
Of course.
I'm not used to being on this side.

51:14.588 --> 51:16.797
-I'm always doing the painting.
-Of course.

51:17.297 --> 51:19.172
And posing is difficult.

51:24.463 --> 51:27.463
-Would you take off your hat?
-Oh, right.

51:27.547 --> 51:29.297
Oh, sorry. Sorry...

51:29.380 --> 51:30.547
Look.

51:30.963 --> 51:31.838
Wow.

51:37.922 --> 51:42.463
You know? I'm not sure how to do this.
Could you help me?

51:42.547 --> 51:43.713
Yeah, sure.

51:47.130 --> 51:51.297
This usually works, although it's a bit
uncomfortable. Move your hip forward.

51:51.380 --> 51:53.213
-OK.
-And stretch your leg out further.

51:53.880 --> 51:55.588
I don't know if this helps.

51:55.963 --> 51:58.880
-These pillows might not be very helpful.
-Right.

52:04.630 --> 52:05.838
Your feet.

52:06.088 --> 52:07.213
-Maybe...
-There.

52:07.297 --> 52:09.797
Let's leave them like this.

52:10.255 --> 52:11.380
Better?

52:24.213 --> 52:28.005
Oh, I'm sorry. It's just being here...

52:28.088 --> 52:32.297
I'm having some kind of connection
with my mother. A memory of her...

52:33.797 --> 52:34.963
Forgive me.

52:35.297 --> 52:36.630
I'm such a fool.

52:39.255 --> 52:40.713
Would you mind giving me a hug?

52:41.713 --> 52:43.463
If that's OK.

52:43.922 --> 52:45.463
You want a hug?

52:45.547 --> 52:47.755
No, it's fine. It doesn't matter.
Forgive me.

52:47.838 --> 52:51.505
I will, of course.
All I want is for you to be comfortable.

52:51.588 --> 52:52.672
All right. Sorry.

52:53.505 --> 52:54.463
OK.

52:55.213 --> 52:56.213
Yeah.

53:00.838 --> 53:02.922
I'm sorry! What happened?

53:03.005 --> 53:04.880
-I don't know...
-Oh, my ring!

53:06.880 --> 53:08.755
-I'm so sorry.
-No, it's all right.

53:15.463 --> 53:18.922
I feel so much better.
I'm more relaxed. Thank you.

53:19.005 --> 53:19.963
I understand you.

53:21.255 --> 53:22.963
I'm also moved.

53:23.047 --> 53:26.172
Having painted your mother moves me.
So does painting you now.

53:47.172 --> 53:48.047
Claudia.

53:49.505 --> 53:50.505
Hey.

53:50.838 --> 53:53.588
-Are you staying over?
-I think so.

53:56.172 --> 53:58.047
You have nothing to be ashamed of.

53:59.505 --> 54:00.505
Well.

54:01.380 --> 54:03.630
A lot is happening in a very short time.

54:06.088 --> 54:09.963
-I lied to my father.
-Technically, I did, not you.

54:12.463 --> 54:14.630
Right, but I couldn't bring myself to...

54:16.422 --> 54:17.297
I don't know.

54:18.088 --> 54:19.630
You'll be ready eventually.

54:20.213 --> 54:21.047
Right?

54:23.380 --> 54:25.297
-Get some rest.
-Thank you.

54:25.713 --> 54:27.338
-Good night.
-Good night.

54:27.422 --> 54:28.880
And good luck tomorrow.

54:45.963 --> 54:47.422
Will you calm down?

54:48.422 --> 54:51.172
I really don't get
how you can be so calm. I mean it.

54:51.255 --> 54:54.588
-He is either your father or mine.
-Well, the test will let us know.

